# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SECRETS — never commit (real API keys + live session cookies)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
/config.env                # root: holds AI_API_KEY — commit config.env.example instead
vendor/*/cookies.json      # live ChatGPT / Gemini session tokens
vendor/*/.env              # bundled-server env (may hold model/creds)
*.pem
*.key
# NOTE: vendor/flow/config.env IS committed on purpose — no secrets (SERVER_API_KEY
# empty), just DEFAULT_PROJECT + ports the Flow server needs to boot.

# ─── runtime workspace (regenerated per video, never commit) ──────────────────
project/
output/
vendor/*/output/

# ─── bundled native binaries — rebuild from source (see README), don't commit ─
# macOS-arm64-only, ~30M. Source: kodelyx/chatgpt-free-api + free-gemini-api.
vendor/*/chatgpt-server
vendor/*/gemini-server

# ─── bundled Flow server runtime (Python/uv) — regenerated, don't commit ──────
vendor/flow/.venv/
vendor/flow/uv.lock

# ─── personal assets (privacy — don't publish) ────────────────────────────────
profile/avatar.jpg
profile/profile.json
profile/topic_history.json

# ─── remotion build artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
remotion/node_modules/
remotion/out/
remotion/public/avatar
remotion/public/broll
remotion/public/sfx
remotion/public/bg_music.mp3
remotion/props/caption.json

# ─── logs / runtime cruft ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
vendor/*/server.log
*.log

# ─── python / editor / os cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.DS_Store
.claude/
.cc-writes/
